13.01	Hardcastle_and_McCormick	Hardcastle and McCormick	Hardcastle and McCormick is a action/drama television series from Stephen J. Cannell Productions, shown on ABC from 1983 through 1986. The series stars Brian Keith as Judge Milton C. Hardcastle and Daniel Hugh Kelly as ex-con and race car driver Mark "Skid" McCormick.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/44/Hardcastle_and_McCormick.png/200px-Hardcastle_and_McCormick.png
